Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 形勢逆轉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:20.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是...!
Comment: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:55.51,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/-------START-------/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:57.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到? 那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:00.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總是很照顧我的一位江湖藝人團的占卜婆婆曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,「擁有刻板世界的人是看不到精靈的」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:09.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...好像是這樣說來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 刻板世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:14.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:16.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恭候光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:20.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救兵嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在發生什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,睜大眼睛 看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是叩拜那些擺設神明也難以看到的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:56.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是神展示在地上的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始我就奔著那裏去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過路上遇到不少阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一直想知道我的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:23.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:28.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...米特蘭西伯爵蘭斯多恩的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:31.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是喜歡狩獵和熱愛獵犬的蘭斯多恩伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了消遣所建成的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前的火災 伯爵及其家臣無一倖免
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在應該是廢墟才對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:47.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來這附近經常發生過路客和朝聖者失蹤的事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是獵犬的下場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:15.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是被血腥味吸引過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:26.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 這種鬼東西...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...不可能存在是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說是奇蹟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如此精彩的場面 你縮起來可如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若是信徒 至少說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,「神啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已經趕上奇蹟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多到都要反胃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟上我 會被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,搞毛 連馬都帶進來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 格斯看來你還沒有知錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一路送我到這裏的那份恩情永生不忘 馬哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人這種生物真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,南無阿彌陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:46.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不尋常的妖魔鬼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這也跟啟示錄的預言有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:27.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我才要問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這座宅邸的飼犬人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:48.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,罷了 總之先幫我把繩解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:50.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我不會虧待你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:51.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為某些緣故落魄至此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是正當的法王廳騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不會做對你不利之事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:06.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吃容易入口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,犬!犬!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別欺負犬!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:31.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...不要傷害我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不可饒恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:36.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是宅邸的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:41.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,敢欺負犬的話 也會成為狗糧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你殺了這裏的主人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:52.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好...好久沒聞到過這麼香的味道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:56.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只有上等貴族女人才有的香味!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:02.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的味道 我...我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,曾是頂級的獵物!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那天的倖存者 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不再為怕撕裂傷口而小心翼翼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不管手臂會因此脫落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我久違地想起來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...那最初的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要感謝你 我現在的心情無比惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:37.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我也感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,終於大駕光臨了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...你很想知道的 我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就是使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使徒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:54.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 將使徒統統殺光一個不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從刻上烙印那一刻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:14.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你...你的命運就決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:19.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,任憑你再怎麼掙扎 最後也只會被獵殺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是弱肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:36.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 別欺負犬!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛呢 格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,像平時那樣干翻他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:02.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉! 肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:16.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我肉太硬 不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:25.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 吃了你之後就吃那個女人來換口味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人跟大小姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:33.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是貴族女人 口感一定很好!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:38.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,入口即溶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:49.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在消滅你們之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:57.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,忤逆我等之人會成為盤中餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 你的吃相也太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:08.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉...肉也有上下等之分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:15.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,善待我之人的肉很柔軟很甘甜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:22.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,罵我醜陋之人的肉是下等!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又臭又硬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那我豈不是不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:31.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不急 馬上見分曉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 這...這...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是真人的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真人剝製而成的標本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不准動!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:12:01.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐...不准你動大小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一...直信任著我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:58.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,醜陋不堪 受盡鄙視的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有大小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一直信任著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:18.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吃剩然後將之漂亮地裝飾供奉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,扭曲到骨子裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:27.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要將使徒獵殺至一個不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,會給你個痛快的招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼才能找到那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,「神之手」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:48.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我對他們一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:58.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的...真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:01.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說了我不知道啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不明所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,頭腦一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,連祈禱的話也想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:17.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:19.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,騎上這匹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:49.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要騎女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雌性 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,美味!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:02.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:30.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死的話就別到處亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:39.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一味亂竄...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...哆嗦著蜷縮起來罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:47.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自稱是神明的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:50.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卻連一句頌揚神明的經文都吟不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已經重複吟唱了成千上萬次...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:01.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...太過渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...可憐而又軟弱無力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是軟弱無力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是軟弱無力 所以沒有罪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別用漂亮話來自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在你心中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有著不可告人的陰暗慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在鞭打那個男人的同時湧起了陰暗的肉慾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:40.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在你自稱為「反省」的鞭打自己之時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:44.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,亦從那痛苦之中感受到了快感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏面沒有神明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:51.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有這種疼痛是真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:54.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你離神明十萬八千里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:02.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:07.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在搞什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 她...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是被惡靈上身了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢舉起這把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起來品嘗...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...這種快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢撕裂我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:19.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:27.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞大人 請您冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但原本的任務是抓住他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:43.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一時感情用事...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就直說了 我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,團長你也看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他那超凡脫俗的強大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只會白白送死...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎喲 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:56.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}團長!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:01.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}你又弄哭了咱家的團長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:02.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:06.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}那麼 我們就此告別
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}如果你肯放我們一馬的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我之前欠你一個人情對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:15.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}拔劍姿勢很高明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}客氣 你才是名不虛傳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}那麼 後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}暫別了 小豆丁也是!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}哼 沒個正經的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}不過 感覺好可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}那個叫法爾納塞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}感覺她渾身都是束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}被五花大綁的是我!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:50.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}繼死靈之後便是僧侶嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}真是鬱悶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:57.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}團長 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:19:59.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}必須殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}必須殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}必須殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}必須封住他的口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}若讓他活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:13.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:23.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人在睡夢中見到了同樣的情境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:27.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一個個為瘟疫所毀滅的村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:32.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是被驅使巨獸的軍隊所蹂躪的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是被地震所摧毀的都市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是被激流所淹沒的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:44.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是被黑煙所遮掩的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是因饑餓而彷徨的人群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:51.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一家人的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是鄰人的屁體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然包羅萬象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卻只有一個內容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在每個不同的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人們都處在相同的黑暗世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,過著真正水深火熱的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而在混沌之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一隻閃閃發光的鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,劈開無盡黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,飛落在鮮血染紅的大地之上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,令他們為之刮目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:29.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是他們所「追尋的希望」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夏洛特 夏洛特...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:42.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,御醫?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:44.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請皇親 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:49.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,終於...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快要誕生一位女王了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夏洛特女王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:56.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,按她的稟性 肯定會任命一位攝政王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙到底明不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:05.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,才贏下了與都鐸的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:06.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:10.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹將重返
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:13.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:15.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所有溫達姆的...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:20.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 所有米特蘭人夢見的不可思議的光之鷹...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:22.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然貴為國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但在多爾多雷攻略戰之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:26.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他的很多行為都高深莫測
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:28.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹之團...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:31.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...真的謀反了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:35.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 請開門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:37.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:43.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拉班將軍 公主把自己關在寢宮整整五天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:46.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能進去的只有一名討她喜歡的侍女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在說服她...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:53.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:08.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:12.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 陛下病危了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:13.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,公主!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:15.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:22.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你個混蛋 現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:30.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,父皇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下升天了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:39.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏在這個時候 今後會變成怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:43.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 格里菲斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:47.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,山在移動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.34,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我知錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.50,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,為了今後 我們要做好相應的計劃...
Comment: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:33.51,OPCht,,0,0,0,,/--------OP---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}燃盡此命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:42.74,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在無盡之夜的夾縫中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:55.62,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}前途暗淡 正張開血盆大口蠢蠢欲動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:01:02.95,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}月之下 染上噩夢的現實無人可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:06.84,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}拿起不折之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:10.39,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}做真實的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:18.03,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}為了不再失去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:28.92,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}流盡此身之血 撕裂傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:36.25,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}掙脫命運 絶不放棄掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:43.54,OPCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}燃盡此命 度過這無盡之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,OPJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}命を燃やし尽くせ
